Comic book style illustration of a lone figure standing on a city rooftop at night, their silhouette bathed in an intense emerald glow emanating from a raised fist. The green energy swirls and forms intricate constructs in the air above them—geometric shapes, shields, and abstract patterns manifesting from pure willpower. The cityscape below is rendered in deep shadows and dramatic angles, with bold ink lines and halftone dot patterns typical of classic comics. The night sky features stars and a crescent moon, while the dominant green light source casts long dramatic shadows across the rooftop. The figure's cape billows in the wind, their posture confident and heroic. Dynamic action lines radiate outward from the glowing energy source, creating a sense of power and imagination made manifest.
